WEBVTT

00:00:28.409 --> 00:00:31.278
un tas ir atrodams 
dažnedažādos ēdienos un dzērienos.

00:00:31.278 --> 00:00:34.212
Vien paskaties uz pirkto saldumu etiķetēm!

00:00:34.212 --> 00:00:34.913
Glikoze,

00:00:34.913 --> 00:00:35.695
fruktoze,

00:00:35.695 --> 00:00:36.627
saharoze,

00:00:36.627 --> 00:00:37.495
maltoze,

00:00:37.495 --> 00:00:38.295
laktoze,

00:00:38.295 --> 00:00:38.969
dekstroze

00:00:38.969 --> 00:00:39.911
un ciete —

00:00:39.911 --> 00:00:41.745
tie visi ir cukura veidi.

00:00:41.745 --> 00:00:43.525
Arī fruktozes kukurūzas sīrups,

00:00:43.525 --> 00:00:44.309
augļu sula,

00:00:44.309 --> 00:00:45.294
jēlcukurs

00:00:45.294 --> 00:00:46.521
un medus.

00:00:46.521 --> 00:00:49.073
Cukurs nav vien saldumos un desertos,

00:00:49.073 --> 00:00:51.188
to pievieno arī tomātu mērcei,

00:00:51.188 --> 00:00:51.846
jogurtam,

00:00:51.846 --> 00:00:52.777
kaltētiem augļiem,

00:00:52.777 --> 00:00:53.856
ūdeņiem ar garšu

00:00:53.856 --> 00:00:55.540
vai musli batoniņiem.

00:00:55.540 --> 00:00:56.995
Tā kā cukurs ir visur,

00:00:56.995 --> 00:00:58.450
ir svarīgi saprast,

00:00:58.450 --> 00:00:59.906
kā tas ietekmē smadzenes.

00:00:59.906 --> 00:01:02.275
Kas notiek, cukuram nonākot uz mēles?